title: BREAKING: White House on lockdown as spooks probe 'bomb threat'
text:
DS LOCKDOWN: Secret Service officals confirmed a "suspicious package" has been found 
Secret Service officals confirmed a "suspicious package" has been found one block from the historic Capitol Hill building in Washington DC. 
MORE TO FOLLOW DON'S DAY: Donald Trump's inauguration as President of The United States Friday, 20th January 2017 Barack Obama officially transfers power to the most controversial US president in modern history as Donald Trump takes to the White House in his inauguration ceremony. 1 / 27 REUTERS US President Donald Trump points to the stands as he walks with his wife Melania during the Inaugural Parade.
